      <title>更多美联储官员准备告别低利率世界</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/more-fed-officials-ready-say-goodbye-low-rate-world-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的美联储官员认为，由于联邦赤字不断膨胀，以及对绿色能源、人工智能和国内制造业的投资需求等各种原因，他们认为不会恢复到 COVID-19 大流行之前普遍存在的超低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/more-fed-officials-ready-say-goodbye-low-rate-world-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
